videos.headline: LSU safety lays out for incredible interception
videos.description: LSU's Grant Delpit plunges towards a deep pass to make an interception on Ole Miss' first drive.

videos.headline: LSU holds moment of silence for basketball player Wayde Sims
videos.description: Before the game, LSU holds a moment of silence in honor of Wayde Sims, who died this week.

videos.headline: LSU WR fights off defender to reel in TD
videos.description: Ja'Marr Chase manages to keep his foot in bounds after fighting off a defender for LSU's first touchdown.

videos.headline: Jefferson finds open field for 65-yard score
videos.description: LSU WR Justin Jefferson takes advantage of busted coverage to take a 65-yard touchdown to the house.

videos.headline: Ole Miss defender ejected after extremely late hit
videos.description: LSU WR Justin Jefferson falls victim to a late hit out-of-bounds, resulting in Ole Miss LB Kevontae' Ruggs getting ejected for targeting.

videos.headline: Skirmish breaks out after late hit on LSU QB
videos.description: LSU QB Joe Burrow scrambles for a 35-yard touchdown, then takes a late hit in the end zone.
